    "description": "Reflect bullets to the beat in this psychedelic rhythm bullet hell shoot 'em up. Patterns of rhythm and bullets are melted into a unprecedented gameplay experience. Feel this immersive audivisual experience filling your soul with excitement and joy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BULLETS FLASH TO THE BEAT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/f8cf9d299e98daa767d6f454e4abf8d2.poster.avif?t=1723887563\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/f8cf9d299e98daa767d6f454e4abf8d2.webm?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/f8cf9d299e98daa767d6f454e4abf8d2.mp4?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Different colors flash to different parts of the beat or melody.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REFLECT BULLETS ON THE BEAT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/aebdefe80df6874f2291ae7956550b00.poster.avif?t=1723887563\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/aebdefe80df6874f2291ae7956550b00.webm?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/aebdefe80df6874f2291ae7956550b00.mp4?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fly near the bullets and hit the button exactly on the beat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/acc28e280f6bdb6a63dd71b78e54d5cf.avif?t=1723887563\" width=600 height=538 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MASTER MELODIES AND BULLET PATTERNS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/a603234696cc79f001b9837ed735e728.poster.avif?t=1723887563\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/a603234696cc79f001b9837ed735e728.webm?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/a603234696cc79f001b9837ed735e728.mp4?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The patterns get more complex with every stage.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAKE COMBOS AND IMPROVE YOUR SCORE EVERY TIME YOU PLAY</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/583e5ed76905a7340f7ddfd44c157853.poster.avif?t=1723887563\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/583e5ed76905a7340f7ddfd44c157853.webm?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/583e5ed76905a7340f7ddfd44c157853.mp4?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you can chain more bullets and make multiple successfull chains in a row you will be rewarded with extra points and lifes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEAT BULLET RAINING BOSSES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/1faa4e24a5878a9d2a9a69c3735d69a9.poster.avif?t=1723887563\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/1faa4e24a5878a9d2a9a69c3735d69a9.webm?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202400/extras/1faa4e24a5878a9d2a9a69c3735d69a9.mp4?t=1723887563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>At the end of every stage a boss is waiting for you with it's own music track.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOUNDSTORM FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 stages with 18 acts. Each is a well crafted audiovisual experience with original gameplay. 30 Minutes of gameplay.<br></li><li>3 difficulty levels: casual, serious, insane. The game is accessible for beginners and offers challenges for shmup otakus.<br></li><li>Deep gameplay and score mechanics keep you coming back for more.<br></li><li>40 Minutes of original music by Nils Künzig. Perfectly synchronised with the stages.<br></li><li>Original hand-drawn thematic artwork by Ziska Renold.<br></li><li>Arcade mode, score attack and custom game modes. </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS </h2><br><strong>Is this a skill based game or a casual game? </strong><br>It's skill based. Easy to learn, hard to master. Each section is unique and leaves room for improvement. The scoring system awards tactics and skills. <br><br><strong>Do you play bullet hell shoot 'em ups? </strong><br>I play bullet hell shoot 'em ups (e.g. from Cave) regularly and understand the deep scoring mechanics those games have. I usually reach the last stage with one credit. I particularly like shooters with innovative concepts like Ikaruga.<br><br><strong>Do you play rhythm games? </strong><br>I used to play rhythm games daily and still play them from time to time. I love how rhythm games force your whole body to be part of the game. This is what I tried to adopt in Soundstorm.",
